parameters:
Maid Dalsa: Today, both Amina and I have been invited to the
dinner party.

Maid Dalsa: Make sure to be respectful! Amina is way too
rude towards Master Luid!
Girl Amina: But... he's just so cute, like a little brother.

Amina's mother, Dalsa, worked as a maid in Luid's house.
Luid's father, Heis, and mother, Caron, treated Amina and
the others like family, rather than as servants.

Amina respected her mother, who worked as a maid, but she
had a strong admiration for Caron.

Amina believed that beauty that seemed to have jumped out of
a painting, and kindness that treated people of our social
status without discrimination, is how a woman should be.

The hatred towards Caron later on was not only because she
was using Luid, but also because her pure childhood
admiration had been tainted.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Maid Amina: I oppose this... What will happen to Lloyd if
you meet with Lady Caron now?

Maid Amina: Lady Caron has become the queen, her world is
already different from ours, you know!?

Young Lloyd: It's not such a big deal. I really like living
here.

Young Lloyd: There's also Auntie here, and most importantly,
Amina is here for me.

Young Lloyd: I just want to meet her... I just want her to
see how much I've grown, that's all.

Suddenly, a letter of invitation arrived for Lloyd from
Queen Caron. Amina opposed it, but she couldn't stop Lloyd.
Later, she would regret not stopping him no matter what he
did.

When Lloyd returned from the palace, he had no vitality at
all. He calmly spoke about abandoning his family name, being
given a new family name, and starting a business of
producing pearls in the new mansion.

Amina was convinced. Lloyd was being asked to do something
other than his public job, and it was something that took
advantage of his pure feelings towards his mother.

Amina decided what she should do. It was to protect Lloyd
from Caron.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
